# Justification: This vulnerability in the cross-spawn package only affects Windows environments. 
# Since we are deploying on an Alpine Linux container, this CVE is not exploitable in our infrastructure.
CVE-2024-21538

# Justification: Unbounded recursive backtracking in minimatch. 
# We do not expose glob pattern inputs to end users, mitigating the DoS risk.
CVE-2026-27903
